fields.description: Re-balance your salt levels during those longer runs. blister pack of 6.

fields.name: Bladder
fields.description: Perfect for keeping hydrated on the move.

fields.name: Buff
fields.description: Machine washable buff. Great for runs in all weather. Use it as a headband to keep the sweat off your brow in the warmer weather. Use it as a snood to keep your warm in the colder weather.

fields.name: Gels
fields.description: High sugar gels to give you the boost you need during those long training run and race day itself. Box of 20. General recommendation is to take one gel every 5-7km. ** Remember the philosophy 'Nothing new on race day'. Always practice taking gels during your training runs so that it will be familiar on race day **
